#: ../../source/cli/overview.rst:4
msgid "`Nest CLI <https://github.com/nestjs/nest-cli>`__ is a command-line interface tool that helps you to to initialize and develop your applications. It helps on many grounds at once, from scaffolding the project to building well-structured apps. The Nest CLI is based on the `Angular Devkit <https://github.com/angular/devkit>`__ package."
msgstr ""

