#: ../../source/cli/usages.rst:26
msgid "The **new** command scaffolds the Nest project based on the `typescript-starter <https://github.com/nestjs/typescript-starter>`__ as well as install the required packages. The CLI will ask you for missing information - the application name (if not specified) and a package manager that you want to use to install dependencies."
